<h2 id="vmd-management-board">
<abbr title="Veterinary Medicines Directorate">VMD</abbr> Management Board</h2>

<p>The Board ensures that effective arrangements are in place to provide assurance on risk management, governance and internal control. It provides:</p>

<ul>
  <li>advice on strategy</li>
  <li>advice on implementation of policies and business objectives</li>
  <li>advice on achieving value for money</li>
  <li>scrutiny of  performance</li>
  <li>support and challenge on the delivery of <abbr title="Veterinary Medicines Directorate">VMD</abbr> responsibilities and the exercise of the <abbr title="Chief Executive Officer">CEO</abbr>’s responsibilities as Accounting Officer (<abbr title="Accounting Officer">AO</abbr>)</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="non-executive-members">Non-executive members</h3>

<h4 id="julia-drown-non-executive-director-and-chair">Julia Drown, non-executive director and chair</h4>

<p><span id="attachment_3300061" class="attachment-inline">
  <a href="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/412517/JuliaDrown.jpg">Julia Drown</a>
  (<span class="type">JPEG</span>, <span class="file-size">28.4KB</span>)
</span></p>

<p>Appointed non-executive Director to the <abbr title="Veterinary Medicines Directorate">VMD</abbr> in May 2014. She is also a trustee of the Nursing and Midwifery Council and Associated Employer’s Pension Scheme and a member of the Human Fertilisation and Embryology Authority (HFEA) Appeals Committee.</p>

<h3 id="david-corner-non-executive-director">David Corner, non-executive director</h3>

<p><span id="attachment_3300060" class="attachment-inline">
  <a href="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/412516/DavidCorner.jpg">David Corner</a>
  (<span class="type">JPEG</span>, <span class="file-size">4.56KB</span>)
</span></p>

<p>Appointed Non-Executive Director to the <abbr title="Veterinary Medicines Directorate">VMD</abbr> in May 2014 and Chairs the Audit and Risk Committee. As a former Director at the National Audit Office and in other roles he has over 25 years’ experience helping to provide assurance to public sector bodies on their financial and operational performance. He is also a non-executive Director at the Wales Audit Office and Chair of their Audit and Risk Management Committee.</p>

<h3 id="david-catlow-non-executive-director">David Catlow, non-executive director</h3>

<p><span id="attachment_3300093" class="attachment-inline">
  <a href="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/767651/CatlowDavid.jpg">David Catlow</a>
  (<span class="type">JPEG</span>, <span class="file-size">32.9KB</span>)
</span></p>

<p>Appointed Non-Executive Director to the <abbr title="Veterinary Medicines Directorate">VMD</abbr> in December 2018. He is a former council member of the Royal College of Veterinary Sugeons (RCVS) and has 30 years’ experience working in a veterinary practice. He is also currently serving as the Director of Clinical Services for the Blue Cross charity.</p>

<h4 id="defra-members">
<abbr title="Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs">Defra</abbr> members</h4>

<ul>
  <li>Christine Middlemiss, Chief Veterinary Officer</li>
  <li>Professor Pete Borriello, <abbr title="Chief Executive Officer">CEO</abbr>, <abbr title="Veterinary Medicines Directorate">VMD</abbr>
</li>
  <li>Paul Green, Director of Operations, <abbr title="Veterinary Medicines Directorate">VMD</abbr>
</li>
  <li>Abigail Seager, Director of Authorisations, <abbr title="Veterinary Medicines Directorate">VMD</abbr>
</li>
  <li>Linda Simmons, Head of Finance, <abbr title="Veterinary Medicines Directorate">VMD</abbr>
</li>
  <li>Mike Griffiths, Head of Business Support Division, <abbr title="Veterinary Medicines Directorate">VMD</abbr>
</li>
</ul>

<p>The Board meets 4 times a year.</p>

