<h2 id="vmd-quarterly-performance-review-board-qprb">
<abbr title="Veterinary Medicines Directorate">VMD</abbr> Quarterly Performance Review Board (<abbr title="quarterly performance review board">QPRB</abbr>)</h2>

<p>The Quarterly Performance Review, chaired by the <abbr title="Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs">Defra</abbr> Chief Operating Officer, facilitates formal reporting on both the <abbr title="Veterinary Medicines Directorate">VMD</abbr>’s delivery of policy objectives and performance against budget. The <abbr title="Veterinary Medicines Directorate">VMD</abbr>’s <abbr title="Chief Executive Officer">CEO</abbr> attends this meeting along with other <abbr title="Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs">Defra</abbr> and <abbr title="Veterinary Medicines Directorate">VMD</abbr> officials as required.</p>

<h2 id="vmd-executive-management-board">
<abbr title="Veterinary Medicines Directorate">VMD</abbr> Executive Management Board</h2>

<p>The board meets weekly to discuss the finances and day-to-day running of the <abbr title="Veterinary Medicines Directorate">VMD</abbr>.</p>

<h3 id="members-1">Members</h3>

<p>The board members are:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Professor Peter Borriello, <abbr title="Chief Executive Officer">CEO</abbr>, <abbr title="Veterinary Medicines Directorate">VMD</abbr>
</li>
  <li>Paul Green, Director of Operations, <abbr title="Veterinary Medicines Directorate">VMD</abbr>
</li>
  <li>Abigail Seager, Director of Authorisations, <abbr title="Veterinary Medicines Directorate">VMD</abbr>
</li>
  <li>Linda Simmons, Head of Finance, <abbr title="Veterinary Medicines Directorate">VMD</abbr>
</li>
  <li>Mike Griffiths, Head of Business Support Division, <abbr title="Veterinary Medicines Directorate">VMD</abbr>
</li>
</ul>

